y 2017|title=New Frontiers in Environmental Constitutionalism|url=https://www.unenvironment.org/sw/node/10714|publisher=UN Environment|location=|page=|isbn=|access-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411234121/https://www.unenvironment.org/sw/node/10714|archive-date=2020-04-11|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Martin 2011\">{{cite book |first= Pamela L.|last= Martin|author-link= |date=2011 |title=Oil in the Soil: The Politics of Paying to Preserve the Amazon |url= |publisher=[[Rowman & Littlefield]] |location= U.S.|page= |isbn=978-1442211285}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Cruz Rodr\u00edguez 2014\">{{cite journal |first1=Edwin |last1=Cruz Rodr\u00edguez |date=2014 |title=Del derecho ambiental a los derechos de la naturaleza: sobre la necesidad del di\u00e1logo intercultural |trans-title=From environmental law to the rights of nature: on the need for intercultural dialogue |language=Spanish |journal=Jur\u00eddicas |publisher=[[University of Caldas]] |location=Manizales, Caldas, Colombia |volume=11 |issue=2 |pages=95-116 |doi= |url=http://juridicas.ucaldas.edu.co/downloads/Juridicas11(1)_6.pdf |access-date=2020-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411234122/http://juridicas.ucaldas.edu.co/downloads/Juridicas11(1)_6.pdf |archive-date=2020-04-11 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Pacari 2009\">{{cite book \u00a0|first=Nina |last=Pacari |author-link= |chapter=Naturaleza y territorio desde la mirada de los pueblos indigenas |trans-chapter= Nature and territory from the perspective of indigenous peoples |editor1-first=Alberto |editor1-last=Acosta |editor1-link= |editor2-first= Esperanza|editor2-last=Martinez|editor2-link=|date=2009 |title= Derechos de la Naturaleza: El Futuro es Ahora |trans-title= Rights of Nature: The Future is Now|url= |publisher=Ediciones Abya-Yala |location=Quito, Ecuador|page= |isbn=978-9978228067}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Tanasescu 2013\">{{cite journal |first1=Mihnea |last1=Tanasescu |first2= |last2= |date=De