i 2016\">{{cite news|first= Mike|last= Gaworecki|date= October 13, 2016|title= Nature\u2019s right to exist gets a boost from key organizations|url= https://news.mongabay.com/2016/10/natures-right-to-exist-gets-a-boost-from-key-organizations/|work= [[Mongabay]]|location= U.S.|access-date= |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200411234119/https://news.mongabay.com/2016/10/natures-right-to-exist-gets-a-boost-from-key-organizations/|archive-date= April 11, 2020|url-status= live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IUCN World Commission on Environmental Law, 2016\">{{cite report |author= [[International Union for Conservation of Nature]], World Commission on Environmental Law |date=2016 |title=Environmental Rule of Law |url=https://www.iucn.org/commissions/world-commission-environmental-law/wcel-resources/environmental-rule-law |publisher=International Union for Conservation of Nature |page= |docket= |access-date= |quote= }}</ref>\n  \n<ref name=\"Sheehan January 24, 2019\">{{cite web |first=Linda |last=Sheehan |title=No one is above nature\u2019s rule of law |url=https://www.leonardodicaprio.org/no-one-is-above-natures-rule-of-law/ |date=January 24, 2019 |website= |publisher=[[Leonardo DiCaprio]] Foundation |access-date= |quote= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411234119/https://www.leonardodicaprio.org/no-one-is-above-natures-rule-of-law/ |archive-date=April 11, 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Kelly 2003\">{{cite book |first=Marjorie |last= Kelly|author-link= |date= 2003|title=The Divine Right of Capital: Dethroning the Corporate Aristocracy |url= |publisher=Berrett-Koehler Publishers |location= |page= |isbn=978-1576752371}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"McKibben 2007\">{{cite book |first=Bill|last=McKibben|author-link=Bill McKibben|date=2007 |title=Deep Economy: The Wealth of Communities and the Durable Future|url= |publisher=[[Henry Holt and Company]]|location= U.S.|page= |isbn=978-0805087222}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Brown & Garver 2009\">{{cite book |first