avarman Thirumulpad Vs. Union of India & Others|url=https://indiankanoon.org/doc/187293069/|date=2012|quote=|access-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205132401/https://indiankanoon.org/doc/187293069/|archive-date=2019-12-05|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Constitution of Ecuador 2008\">{{cite web|author=Republic of Ecuador|author-link=Ecuador|title=Constitution, Chapter 7|url=http://pdba.georgetown.edu/Constitutions/Ecuador/english08.html|date=2008|quote=|access-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511121607/http://pdba.georgetown.edu/Constitutions/Ecuador/english08.html|archive-date=2019-05-11|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Boori 2015\">{{cite news |first=Aisha |last=Bhoori |date=June 17, 2015 |title=How Pope Francis Hinted At His Climate Change Encyclical |url=https://time.com/3925143/pope-francis-environmentalist/ |work=[[Time (magazine)|Time]] |location=U.S. |access-date= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730061319/https://time.com/3925143/pope-francis-environmentalist/ |archive-date=July 30, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Vidal 2014\">{{cite news |first=John |last=Vidal |date=December 27, 2014 |title=Pope Francis\u2019s edict on climate change will anger deniers and US churches |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/dec/27/pope-francis-edict-climate-change-us-rightwing |work=[[The Guardian]] |location=U.K. |access-date= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220082620/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/dec/27/pope-francis-edict-climate-change-us-rightwing |archive-date=February 20, 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Pope Francis 2014\">{{cite web |url=http://www.usccb.org/_cs_upload/issues-and-action/human-life-and-dignity/environment/175525_2.pdf |title=Address to Participants in the World Meeting of Popular Movements (in U.S. Conference of Catholic Bishops, Environmental Quotes: On Caring for God\u2019s Creation) |author=[[Pope Francis]] |da